    %h3 Summer Expo
    %h6 July 12th, 2015
    %h6 1pm - 7pm
    %h6 Institute for Innovation, University of California Irvine
    %h6 5141 California Ave. Irvine, CA

  .section
    %p Join us for a day of immersion with the world of virtual reality. Experience exciting VR content brought in from all over of Southern California and beyond. The day will be filled with demos, panels, and giveaways.
    %p SoCal VR is a collection of content creators, developers, film makers, journalists, audio professionals, engineers, artists, and creative people every where in between. Those who buy VIP tickets will get access to the demo floor 2 hours early and can sit in on the VIP panel at noon.

